 CellChangeTimes->{3.395533712743822*^9}]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["In polar coordinates, our problem, therefore, is to solve", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.3955342749144297`*^9, 3.395534297705014*^9}}],

Cell[BoxData[
 StyleBox[
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
