  FontColor->GrayLevel[0.5]]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.395536657185524*^9, 3.3955366690246964`*^9}}],

Cell["which forces us to insist that", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.39553669766324*^9, 3.395536720694322*^9}}],

